Framework Setup

1. TDD - Test Driven Development
2. BDD - Behavior Driven Development
3. Keyword driven
4. Hybrid


Source Folders
src/test/java  ==> test cases
src/test/resources  ==> test data file or any test file

src/main/java  ==> contain the logic
src/main/resources  ==> config or properties file

Design Patterns:
POM: Page Object Model
Singleton

UTIL
Excel Reader
Screenshot
base code
logging
reports


--------
test case
knows:
 what we are testing
 what is the test data
 what is the expected result
does not know:
 how to test it/perform the action
 actual result
 
 
 -------------------------------------Git
 GIT
 open terminal/cmd
 go to your project folder
 git init >> Initialized empty Git repository
 git status >> check what are the new changes and status
 git add .  >> move all the untracked changes to staging area
 git commit -m "message"
 git remote add origin link >> this is required only one time, setup
 git push origin master
 
 
 
 

